# 🏥 醫療衛教平台程式碼擁有者設定
# 此檔案定義了不同檔案和目錄的審核者
# 當 PR 涉及這些檔案時，會自動指派相應的審核者

# 全域預設審核者
* @tech-team @content-manager

# 醫療內容審核
# 所有衛教內容都需要醫療專業審核
src/content/education/ @medical-advisors @content-team

# 專科特定內容審核
src/content/education/*cardiology* @cardiology-reviewer @medical-advisors
src/content/education/*neurology* @neurology-reviewer @medical-advisors  
src/content/education/*pediatrics* @pediatrics-reviewer @medical-advisors
src/content/education/*emergency* @emergency-reviewer @medical-advisors
src/content/education/*orthopedics* @orthopedics-reviewer @medical-advisors

# 醫療專科配置檔案
